<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="ldexp" id="ldexp">ldexp</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

Syntax:

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
&nbsp;
    <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">ldexp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">float</span> n, <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">ldexp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> n, <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">ldexp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> n, <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
Computes floating point value from significand and exponent.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "ldexp" [1-254] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2"><a name="parameters" id="parameters">Parameters</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

<code>n</code> - floating point value representing significand
</p>

<p>
<code>exp</code> - floating point value representing exponent
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "Parameters" [255-383] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="return_value" id="return_value">Return value</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

floating point value composed from significand and exponent (<code>num * (2 ^ exp)</code>)
</p>

<p>
If the return type is too small for the result, range error occurs and <code>HUGE_VAL</code> is returned.
</p>

</div>
